### CSS Overview (styles.css)

The stylesheet defines:

* CSS Variables

Used for theme colors, shadows, spacing and fonts.

* Global Styles

Box-sizing
Typography
Smooth rendering

* Layout Tools

- container for max-width layout
- grid and .flex sections

Responsive media queries for ≥700px and ≥1024px

* Component Styles

Navigation
Hero banner
Cards
Tracks grid
Speaker cards
Sponsor logo hover effects
Form styling
Footer and contact section

* Accessibility

Focus outline styling
Skip-link visibility

### How to Use / Run the Website

Download all files
Make sure index.html and styles.css are in the same directory
Ensure assets (images) are inside an img folder
Open index.html in a browser
(Optional) Upload to GitHub Pages, Netlify, or Vercel

### Future Enhancements (Optional)

Add JavaScript for animations
Add registration backend (Firebase, Supabase, PHP, etc.)
Implement dark mode toggle
Add countdown timer for the event

